The solution was to add a global `omnisharp.json` file in `%USERPROFILE%/.omnisharp/` and enable the editorconfig support there. 
```json
{
  "FormattingOptions": {
    "EnableEditorConfigSupport": true
  }
}
```
More information here: https://github.com/OmniSharp/omnisharp-roslyn/wiki/Configuration-Options

I'm not sure what this means, but I think that the configuration is not properly passed to omnisharp and I dosen't respect the .editorconfig file.
